| first2 = MS
| last3 = Hallstrom
| first3 = AP
| last4 = Litwin
| first4 = PE
| issue = 2}}</ref> Yet there are cases of patients regaining consciousness during CPR while still in full cardiac arrest.<ref>{{cite journal
| last = Lewinter JR et al.
| title = CPR-dependent consciousness: evidence for cardiac compression causing forward flow
