| number=5 
| pages=138–142 
| year=2010 
| doi=10.1093/bjaceaccp/mkq024 
| url=http://ceaccp.oxfordjournals.org/content/10/5/138.full
| eprint=http://ceaccp.oxfordjournals.org/content/10/5/138.full.pdf+html}}
</ref>
Longer durations are possible at lower temperatures, but the usefulness of longer procedures has not been established yet.<ref name="M.D2010">{{cite book
